name: THEKEY
description: THEKEY (TKY) project team aims to create an identification verification (IDV) tool on the NEO blockchain. THEKEY IDV tool will feature a dynamic multi-dimension identification (BDMI) by using Personally Identifiable Information (PII) authorized by governments. The IDV tool has reportedly been deployed for mobile social insurance in two pilot cities where people can receive payments for pensions or healthcare insurance reimbursement.
